{"tid":54664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正字撚入黎","createTime":"2016-12-25T17:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T17:59:32.000Z","uid":54132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d404e8ba569a980527a99fca31ab9d057dedda55","tid":54664,"uid":54132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T17:28:37.000Z","msg":"想問下如果問句用個(那)字，例如以下(那)一個答案是正確的？<br />\n個(那)字算唔算係別字？<br />\n我知道(哪)係通常用係問句<br />\n但漢語詞典又寫其實(那)係可以包含(哪)既意思，呢種情況應該點？<br />\n用(那)字係問句又會否好奇怪顯眼？"},{"pid":"c137e72a4942622077909bf0ac0c283dadfbdf5f","tid":54664,"uid":54132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T17:29:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53a5aa817e53b089e3ea842a33244ce7e8e92d1","tid":54664,"uid":54132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T17:29:15.000Z","msg":"yoyoyo"},{"pid":"81d77687286937fa0d684eba73df02a7cdda46e5","tid":54664,"uid":54132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T17:30:44.000Z","msg":"高登班正字撚原來都係偽毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出哂去玩"},{"pid":"350d243542ee36ddf7b5a48a9e647011531915df","tid":54664,"uid":54132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T17:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高登班正字撚原來都係偽毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出哂去玩</blockquote><br />\n連登先岩，手快打錯"},{"pid":"1a17d3ae6e1ce0a323f3dcea17e489e254a75191","tid":54664,"uid":54132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T17:32:07.000Z","msg":"正經問野冇人理"},{"pid":"761551511b4ec0953595c62af3d9bdb3714443fd","tid":54664,"uid":42082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T17:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正經問野冇人理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你幾分鐘前問<br />\n唔通你要我地秒秒鐘都係度等你出post跟住秒回你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問句用「哪」<br />\n果一個用「那」<br />\n可以當係英文入面嘅which one 同埋that one<br />\n有插勿插<br />\n留名學野